Important implementation details:

- the fluid flexbox is not a single element, there is a wrapper as well the className is apied to the flexbox, but you can style the wrapper as well
- might be needed and useful in a case where the fluidflexbox is inside a flex container, and you want to to grow for example (see "Nested" example),
